{"id":200,"parent_id":196,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":200,"title":"1 Thessalonians 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Thes.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","The Saints are told to be holy, sanctify themselves, and love one another—The Lord will come, and the dead will rise."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.1","order":"03.15.004.21581"},["b","1"],"Furthermore then we beseech you, brethren, and exhort",["i","you"],"by the Lord Jesus, that as ye have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"received"],"of us how ye ought to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"walk"],"and to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"please"],"God,",["i","so"],"ye would",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"abound"],"more and more."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.2","order":"03.15.004.21582"},["b","2"],"For ye know what commandments",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"we"],"gave you by the Lord Jesus."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.3","order":"03.15.004.21583"},["b","3"],"For this is the will of God,",["i","even"],"your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"sanctification"],", that ye should",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"abstain"],"from",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"fornication"],":"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.4","order":"03.15.004.21584"},["b","4"],"That every one of you should know how to possess his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"vessel"],"in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"sanctification"],"and honour;"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.5","order":"03.15.004.21585"},["b","5"],"Not in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"lust of concupiscence"],", even as the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"Gentiles"],"which",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"know not"],"God:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.6","order":"03.15.004.21586"},["b","6"],"That no",["i","man"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"go beyond and defraud"],"his brother in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},["i","any"],"matter"],": because that the Lord",["i","is"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"avenger"],"of all such, as we also have forewarned you and testified."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.7","order":"03.15.004.21587"},["b","7"],"For God hath not called us unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"uncleanness"],", but unto holiness."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.8","order":"03.15.004.21588"},["b","8"],"He therefore that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"despiseth"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"despiseth"],"not man, but God, who hath also given unto us his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"holy Spirit"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.9","order":"03.15.004.21589"},["b","9"],"But as touching",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"brotherly love"],"ye need not that I write unto you: for ye yourselves are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"taught"],"of God to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"love"],"one another."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.10","order":"03.15.004.21590"},["b","10"],"And indeed ye do it toward all the brethren which are in all Macedonia: but we beseech you, brethren, that ye increase more and more;"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.11","order":"03.15.004.21591"},["b","11"],"And that ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"study"],"to be quiet, and to do your own business, and to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"work"],"with your own",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"hands"],", as we commanded you;"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.12","order":"03.15.004.21592"},["b","12"],"That ye may walk",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"honestly"],"toward them that are without, and",["i","that"],"ye may have lack of nothing."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.13","order":"03.15.004.21593"},["b","13"],"But I would not have you to be ignorant, brethren, concerning them which are asleep, that ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"sorrow"],"not, even as others which have no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"hope"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.14","order":"03.15.004.21594"},["b","14"],"For if we believe that Jesus died and rose again, even so them also which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"sleep"],"in Jesus will God bring with him."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.15","order":"03.15.004.21595"},["b","15"],"For this we say unto you by the word of the Lord,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"that"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"we"],"which are alive",["i","and"],"remain unto the coming of the Lord shall not",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"prevent"],"them which are asleep."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.16","order":"03.15.004.21596"},["b","16"],"For the Lord himself shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"descend"],"from heaven with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"a shout"],", with the voice of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"archangel"],", and with the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_16d"},"trump"],"of God: and the dead in Christ shall",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_16e"},"rise"],"first:"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.17","order":"03.15.004.21597"},["b","17"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Then"],"we which are alive",["i","and"],"remain shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"caught up"],"together with them in the clouds, to meet the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"Lord"],"in the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_17d"},"air"],": and so shall we",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_17e"},"ever"],"be with the",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_17f"},"Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.18","order":"03.15.004.21598"},["b","18"],"Wherefore comfort one another with these words."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.1a","order":"03.15.004.21599"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/4.9"},"Philip. 4:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.1b","order":"03.15.004.21601"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.1c","order":"03.15.004.21603"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/1.10"},"Col. 1:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.1d","order":"03.15.004.21605"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/3.12"},"1 Thes. 3:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.2a","order":"03.15.004.21607"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.38"},"D&C 1:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.3a","order":"03.15.004.21609"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/12.14"},"Heb. 12:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.3b","order":"03.15.004.21611"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/abstain"},"TG Abstain"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.3c","order":"03.15.004.21613"},["b","3c"],["span.small","GR"],"immorality.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/chastity"},"TG Chastity"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fornication"},"Fornication"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sexual-immorality"},"Sexual Immorality"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/whore"},"Whore"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.4a","order":"03.15.004.21615"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/body-sanctity-of"},"TG Body, Sanctity of"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.4b","order":"03.15.004.21617"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sanctification"},"TG Sanctification"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.5a","order":"03.15.004.21619"},["b","5a"],["span.small","GR"],"passion of lust.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lust"},"TG Lust"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-husbands"},"Marriage, Husbands"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.5b","order":"03.15.004.21621"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/4.17.17,19"},"Eph. 4:17 (17, 19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.5c","order":"03.15.004.21623"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/2.12.11-12"},"Eph. 2:12 (11–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.6a","order":"03.15.004.21625"},["b","6a"],["span.small","GR"],"take advantage of, wrong."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.6b","order":"03.15.004.21627"},["b","6b"],["span.small","GR"],"the matter."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.6c","order":"03.15.004.21629"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/1.8"},"2 Thes. 1:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.7a","order":"03.15.004.21631"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/uncleanness"},"TG Uncleanness"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.8a","order":"03.15.004.21633"},["b","8a"],["span.small","GR"],"rejects, sets aside, violates."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.8b","order":"03.15.004.21635"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/10.16"},"Luke 10:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.8c","order":"03.15.004.21637"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.10"},"1 Cor. 2:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/3.24"},"1 Jn. 3:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.9a","order":"03.15.004.21639"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/brotherhood-and-sisterhood"},"TG Brotherhood and Sisterhood"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.9b","order":"03.15.004.21641"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/6.45"},"John 6:45"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/2.27.20,27"},"1 Jn. 2:27 (20, 27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.9c","order":"03.15.004.21643"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"TG Love"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.11a","order":"03.15.004.21645"},["b","11a"],["span.small","GR"],"strive, endeavor earnestly."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.11b","order":"03.15.004.21647"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/industry"},"TG Industry"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/labor"},"Labor"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/skill"},"Skill"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/work-value-of"},"Work, Value of"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.11c","order":"03.15.004.21649"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/31.13"},"Prov. 31:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.12a","order":"03.15.004.21651"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/dependability"},"TG Dependability"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honesty"},"Honesty"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.13a","order":"03.15.004.21653"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/despair"},"TG Despair"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mourning"},"Mourning"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sorrow"},"Sorrow"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.13b","order":"03.15.004.21655"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/2.12"},"Eph. 2:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.14a","order":"03.15.004.21657"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/14.5"},"Zech. 14:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.15a","order":"03.15.004.21659"},["b","15a"],["span.small","JST"],"1 Thes. 4:15 … that",["i","they who"],"are alive",["i","at"],"the coming of the Lord, shall not prevent them",["i","who remain unto the coming of the Lord, who"],"are asleep."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.15b","order":"03.15.004.21661"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/2.2.1-3"},"2 Thes. 2:2 (1–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.15c","order":"03.15.004.21663"},["b","15c"],["span.small","GR"],"precede, make progress over."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.16a","order":"03.15.004.21665"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"},"TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.16b","order":"03.15.004.21667"},["b","16b"],["span.small","GR"],"a cry of command, a cheer."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.16c","order":"03.15.004.21669"},["b","16c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/adam"},"TG Adam"],"."],["div",{"id":"16d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.16d","order":"03.15.004.21671"},["b","16d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/24.31"},"Matt. 24:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"16e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.16e","order":"03.15.004.21673"},["b","16e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/resurrection"},"TG Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.17a","order":"03.15.004.21675"},["b","17a"],["span.small","JST"],"1 Thes. 4:17 Then",["i","they who"],"are alive, shall be caught up together",["i","into"],"the clouds",["i","with them who remain,"],"to meet the Lord in the air; and so shall we be ever with the Lord."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.17b","order":"03.15.004.21677"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/15.51"},"1 Cor. 15:51"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.96.96-97"},"D&C 88:96 (96–97)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.31"},"101:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/109.75"},"109:75"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.17c","order":"03.15.004.21679"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/jude/1.14.14-16"},"Jude 1:14 (14–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.17d","order":"03.15.004.21681"},["b","17d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.34"},"Moro. 10:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"17e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.17e","order":"03.15.004.21683"},["b","17e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/immortality"},"TG Immortality"],"."],["div",{"id":"17f","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/4.17f","order":"03.15.004.21685"},["b","17f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/14.3"},"John 14:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/22.4.3-5"},"Rev. 22:4 (3–5)"],"."]]}
